values: Lust and passion are not synonymous.
The flowers smell of summer love.
Goddess, wants V-Day date. Male? Female?
Passion overflows beyond one single day.
Without passion there is no existence.

I have never before been to Earth except a short trip to Las Vegas and the opera. I must admit I am intrigued by how your people view love, lust, passion. I am Li and I embody all of those things and so much more. I am not human or even a goddess of your planet. My people, the Centauri hail from far away among the stars.

I do hope I will learn what it is that brings my splendor to your people.
